result.name: La Piazza

reviews.text: Very good Italian food, hidden gem in Hang Hau village. Decor is great, good music and vibe. Service is attentive and friendly. Difficult to find parking here, but walking distance from MTR.
I orderd a smoke salmon salad, penne blogndse, and parter orderd a lunch course menu, onion soup and beef steak. We also had a apple tarte. Very tasty! It is worth to visit!
Very good food and management
Nice pizza and pasta.  Reasonably priced.

This is a small restaurant with indoor outdoor dining. Really nice food, great for families or couples. Good quality house wines. My favourite, Cajun Chicken pizza with a Greek salad. Take away available.

簿餅好正下次再試其他味，質素唔錯🖒
